        </User>
        <Sticky classid="Sticky" id="1435527686" x="1926" y="918" w="486" h="414" colors="0, 15792890">
          <paramlist>
            <param name="full_font" value="Tahoma, 9pt" />
            <param name="align" value="0" />
            <param name="style" value="1" />
            <param name="font" value="1" />
            <param name="fg_color" value="0" />
            <param name="bg_color" value="15792890" />
            <param name="arrows" value="0" />
            <param name="opacity" value="25" />
          </paramlist><![CDATA[BESS_Fault02:
1- The "Upstream" Architecture: Adding the AC Grid & Rectifier
BESS_Fault03:
2- Protection Coordination (Relay Logic)
BESS_Fault04:
3- The Dynamic Catenary (Moving Train Physics)
(-- 1km --> R_Line = 0.05ohm &  L_Line = 0.002H)
(-- 5km --> R_Line = 0.25ohm &  L_Line = 0.01H)
(-- 10km --> R_Line = 0.5ohm &  L_Line = 0.02H)
BESS_Fault05:
4- Active Control
Test 1 (Acceleration): A 3.0 Ohm load resistor at the end of the line (where the train is) to act like a traction motor.

Test 2 (Regen Braking): A standard DC Voltage Source at the end of the line (where the train is) and set it to 3.3 kV to act like a train violently braking.]]></Sticky>
        <User classid="UserCmp" defn="master:breaker1" id="415900577" x="1620" y="378" w="95" h="33" z="650" orient="0" link="-1" q="4">
